<br/><strong><a href="https://issues.shopware.com/issues/NEXT-6319" target="_blank">NEXT-6319</a> - </strong>You can now clear the cache via the administration.
<br/><strong><a href="https://issues.shopware.com/issues/NEXT-6425" target="_blank">NEXT-6425</a> - </strong>CartBehavior::isRecalculation deprecation New way over permissions
